{"tid":2086713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Reddit封鎖支持特朗普討論群組","createTime":"2020-06-30T11:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:07:28.000Z","uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b82098bfb8a8599d5138955e2d3f8a94262d375","tid":2086713,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/29110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F29110&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F0UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=9366bfc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F29110&h=71a902e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/29110</a><br />\n<br />\n美國最大網上討論區Reddit，周一封鎖了約二千個討論群組，包括一個支持總統特朗普的討論群組版面，指群組持續鼓吹暴力，騷擾其他用戶，違反討論區的內容政策。<br />\n<br />\n但群組上一次發貼文，已經是多個月前，早就另起爐灶，設置了新網站和社交賬戶，更於Reddit下封鎖令後，語帶嘲諷說「沒有了版面，不知道該怎麼辦」。<br />\n<br />\n群組被封鎖前，於Reddit有逾79萬用戶，不少在其他社交平台瘋傳，由網民製作，支持特朗普的片段和圖片，均是來自此群組。特朗普的競選團隊就經常瀏覽群組的版面，留意選情的最新發展。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜旗下的直播平台Twitch，同日亦暫停特朗普的官方頻道，指部分造勢活動片段的留言涉及仇恨，已經刪除冒犯的內容，但未有明言何時解封頻道。"},{"pid":"f54aa92d36ddc6135b9102bc8e8fb3c86f4bceeb","tid":2086713,"uid":6103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"全面封殺侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01271177df39034c309e53092b55485d2e4e07a5","tid":2086713,"uid":143343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:37:11.000Z","msg":"同中國做既野一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba77f517bea6ac0a59c08f524d38268dbba5f3b","tid":2086713,"uid":78304,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"騰訊出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6faca1cf8814ec05d15ad3748e05eb664cd4ef9","tid":2086713,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"騰訊ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21e7625d37d40b10cb9374a0dcec35abaacfea0","tid":2086713,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我想破2千正評, 留個紀念得唔得"},{"pid":"13348804b3ea2b099d0b0242edaf478c5cc4a24f","tid":2086713,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"根本就另類中共，中國就中共話事，美國就左膠話事，屈你散播仇恨，種族歧視，逼啲商家佬企佢個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}